    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:16">This topic covers some of the most frequent questions we get from technical
        documentation writer teams willing to investigate the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="b:1;6:66">Oxygen XML</b> set of tools as a
        possible solution for writing and publishing content.</shortdesc>
