                                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="p:12;92:44">The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="b:23;92:51">Oxygen XML Author</b> allows writers to visually
                                            edit <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="b:24;93:53">DITA XML</b> content and to publish it to
