                                        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="p:14;101:44">A video of how <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="b:27;101:62">Content Fusion</b> Works: <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/content_fusion/take_a_tour.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/oxygen_xml_as_a_technical_documentation_solution_faq.dita" xtrc="xref:10;103:81"/>.</p>
